rows.label: qev041502_MSG0001
rows.name: Hmm? Wait, do I...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0002
rows.name: Hello again, shiny lady![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0003
rows.name: Gya! You're that Nopon! Gosh, this brings me back...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0004
rows.name:
Long time no see. And many apologizings for—ACK!
Head of lady![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0005
rows.name: Head of lady has HAIR![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0006
rows.name: ...Huh? Ooooooh. Riiiiiiight. This.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0007
rows.name:
Yeaaah, so once I stopped to think about it,
we're all just mimeosomes, yeah?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0008
rows.name:
Turns out hair is, like, super easy to swap out.
I mean, it's basically a wig anyway, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0009
rows.name:
And as it turns out, going full cue ball gave me the
push I needed to try a totally new hairstyle!
Funny story, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0010
rows.name:
*sniff* Chiroro in mild shock. All that time to find
recipe for cure. All those brushes with toothy death
gathering ingredients...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0011
rows.name:
Er, sorry? Not sure I follow, but, um, yeah.
Oof. Sounds...rough.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0012
rows.name:
Hrmmm. Well, Chiroro still want to properly pay
back no-longer-shiny lady.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0013
rows.name: Taking care of customers is foundation of any business![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0014
rows.name:
Chiroro will go sell off these ingredients.
They are not worth full 10,000 credits,
but should still be nothing to sneeze at.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0015
rows.name: What? No, hey...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0016
rows.name: Just wait little bit longer, hairy lady![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0017
rows.name:
Chiroro will be back with cash in flash!
...Oh, hey. That rhyme.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0018
rows.name: I said WAIT a second![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0019
rows.name: Buh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0020
rows.name:
Look, I don't care about the money anymore.
You've made a clear show of your sincerity here,
and I appreciate it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0021
rows.name: Hrmrmrurur?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0022
rows.name:
You worked hard running around to find that stuff,
and now you're just going to turn around and sell it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0023
rows.name: But nice hairy lady deserve—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0024
rows.name:
Wow. You have SOLD ME on the Nopon, buddy!
That is some seriously fantastic customer service.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0025
rows.name: Let's call it square, Chiroro.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0026
rows.name: R-really?! Oh, thank you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0027
rows.name:
Sure thing. Keep this up, and I'm sure you'll make
it big as a merchant.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041502_MSG0028
rows.name:
And when that happen, Chiroro hope nice hairy
lady becomes regular customer![ST:wait ]
